Subject: [PATCH] ALSA: hda - Add mute-LED mode control to Thinkpad
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 7290006d8c0900c56d8c58428134f02c35109d17
